body:
Program Duration: {{program.duration}}
Start Date: {{program.start_date}}
End Date: {{program.end_date}}

Schedule Details:
- Meeting Days: {{meeting_days}}
- Meeting Times: {{meeting_times}}
- Location: {{program.location}}
- Total Hours: {{total_hours}} hours

The program schedule may be subject to modifications with {{notice_period}} days written notice.

Any intellectual property, research findings, or creative works developed during the program shall be governed as follows:

a) Pre-existing IP remains with original owner
b) Program-related IP: {{ip_ownership}}
c) Joint discoveries: {{joint_ip_terms}}
d) Publication rights: {{publication_rights}}
e) Attribution requirements: {{attribution_policy}}

Participants agree to disclose any potential IP conflicts before program commencement.

Financial Arrangements:

Stipend Amount: {{stipend_amount}} per {{stipend_frequency}}
Payment Schedule: {{payment_schedule}}
Payment Method: {{payment_method}}

Additional Benefits:
- Travel allowance: {{travel_allowance}}
- Meal allowance: {{meal_allowance}}
- Equipment provided: {{equipment_provided}}
- Insurance coverage: {{insurance_coverage}}

Tax obligations are the responsibility of the Participant.

Any disputes arising from this agreement shall be resolved through:

1. Direct discussion between parties
2. Mediation through {{mediation_service}}
3. Arbitration if mediation fails
4. Legal proceedings as a last resort

Governing Law: {{governing_law}}
Jurisdiction: {{jurisdiction_location}}

Both parties agree to attempt resolution in good faith before pursuing formal legal action.
